        <h3 class="node-title card-project__title">
            <a href="/project/arise-ii-advancing-research-science-and-engineering-role-academia-industry-and-government" rel="bookmark"><span class="project__title project__title--card">ARISE II—Advancing Research In Science and Engineering: The Role of Academia, Industry, and Government in the 21st Century</span>
</a>
        </h3>
        <div class="project__teaser project__teaser--card field field-node--field-teaser field-name-field-teaser field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item"><p>The ARISE II project&nbsp;developed&nbsp;actionable recommendations to sustain a competitive U.S. research enterprise. This work was designed to&nbsp;foster new relationships across the disciplines and between the private and public sectors.</p>
</div>
      </div>
</div>

